{
  "video_id": "KWnV1Aa6VQ8",
  "title": "A conversation on migration",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 1964.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16468.0,
      "end_time": 17676.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: Good morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17676.0,
      "end_time": 18200.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18200.0,
      "end_time": 18657.0,
      "text": "How are you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18658.0,
      "end_time": 19149.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: How are you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19149.0,
      "end_time": 19640.0,
      "text": "SUBJECT: Coffee all?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19640.0,
      "end_time": 20150.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20150.0,
      "end_time": 21729.0,
      "text": "Coffee would be great, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21730.0,
      "end_time": 22150.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: Me too, please."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 22150.0,
      "end_time": 22776.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22777.0,
      "end_time": 24610.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: You know, the whole question"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24610.0,
      "end_time": 27900.0,
      "text": "of migration through the ages --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27100.0,
      "end_time": 28660.0,
      "text": "since biblical times, we&#39;ve had it."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28660.0,
      "end_time": 32439.0,
      "text": "But now, in our lived history, we have a refugee crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 32439.0,
      "end_time": 36370.0,
      "text": "We have more migration than we&#39;ve had since World War II."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36370.0,
      "end_time": 38379.0,
      "text": "And I started thinking about this community"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 38380.0,
      "end_time": 40320.0,
      "text": "and the possibility of having one"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40320.0,
      "end_time": 43810.0,
      "text": "in doing my own work on translation studies but also"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43810.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "literary history and started to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50410.0,
      "text": "how much I needed to know to talk about some"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 50410.0,
      "end_time": 52550.0,
      "text": "of these things in the current period."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 52550.0,
      "end_time": 54940.0,
      "text": "So I went to a couple of colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 54940.0,
      "end_time": 58360.0,
      "text": "and talked with them, learned a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 58360.0,
      "end_time": 60700.0,
      "text": "and started to think about how much"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60700.0,
      "end_time": 62770.0,
      "text": "it would mean to have a group of faculty"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 62770.0,
      "end_time": 66520.0,
      "text": "from roundabout campus who could talk about these things"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 66520.0,
      "end_time": 70240.0,
      "text": "and, in innovative ways, share knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 70240.0,
      "end_time": 73240.0,
      "text": "share ways of thinking about this issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73240.0,
      "end_time": 77800.0,
      "text": "and how, eventually, this could have a huge ripple effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 77800.0,
      "end_time": 79929.0,
      "text": "on campus through our teaching, through having"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 79930.0,
      "end_time": 83110.0,
      "text": "student affiliates, graduate and undergraduates."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83110.0,
      "end_time": 86860.0,
      "text": "And, perhaps, over time, we will see"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86860.0,
      "end_time": 90280.0,
      "text": "opportunities for changing the public discourse"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 90280.0,
      "end_time": 92230.0,
      "text": "and developing it into something that"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92230.0,
      "end_time": 95530.0,
      "text": "can create better solutions or at least"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95530.0,
      "end_time": 96816.0,
      "text": "better debates about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96816.0,
      "end_time": 97690.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 97690.0,
      "end_time": 100570.0,
      "text": "We probably need to understand why people see this issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 100570.0,
      "end_time": 103860.0,
      "text": "you know, so differently, disagree so widely --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103860.0,
      "end_time": 106000.0,
      "text": "where they&#39;re coming from, what their perceptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 106000.0,
      "end_time": 108100.0,
      "text": "are, what their misperceptions are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108100.0,
      "end_time": 109842.0,
      "text": "and how this can be clarified."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 109842.0,
      "end_time": 111550.0,
      "text": "One of the things I find most interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 111550.0,
      "end_time": 113200.0,
      "text": "is that this is an issue that doesn&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 113200.0,
      "end_time": 116950.0,
      "text": "cut across the usual left-right divide cleanly."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 116950.0,
      "end_time": 120220.0,
      "text": "There are liberals that worry about high levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 120220.0,
      "end_time": 123364.0,
      "text": "of immigration because of the impact on the working class."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 123364.0,
      "end_time": 124780.0,
      "text": "There are conservatives that worry"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124780.0,
      "end_time": 127220.0,
      "text": "about high levels of immigration both for that reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 127220.0,
      "end_time": 129770.0,
      "text": "but also because of effects on the culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 129770.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132672.0,
      "text": "and because of concerns about cultural stability."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132672.0,
      "end_time": 134380.0,
      "text": "On the other hand, there are progressives"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 134380.0,
      "end_time": 138220.0,
      "text": "that are in favor, of course, of high levels of immigration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 138220.0,
      "end_time": 140380.0,
      "text": "generous policy towards refugees and poorer"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 140380.0,
      "end_time": 141377.0,
      "text": "migrants from abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141377.0,
      "end_time": 142960.0,
      "text": "And, likewise, there are conservatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 142960.0,
      "end_time": 146800.0,
      "text": "who believe in open markets and open borders, a little"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146800.0,
      "end_time": 147310.0,
      "text": "more libertarian."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 147310.0,
      "end_time": 149740.0,
      "text": "So these issues are difficult ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 149740.0,
      "end_time": 152470.0,
      "text": "for both of the major political parties, in a way."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 152470.0,
      "end_time": 154379.0,
      "text": "And it makes them interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154379.0,
      "end_time": 155920.0,
      "text": "Then the question of who is a refugee"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 155920.0,
      "end_time": 159130.0,
      "text": "is a central one that hasn&#39;t been all together settled."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159130.0,
      "end_time": 162340.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a disputed category in international law."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162340.0,
      "end_time": 167990.0,
      "text": "And are people that move out of great poverty refugees"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 167990.0,
      "end_time": 169900.0,
      "text": "or merely economic migrants?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 169900.0,
      "end_time": 172220.0,
      "text": "A lot of these issues need a lot more attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 172220.0,
      "end_time": 173471.0,
      "text": "as a matter of policy and law."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173471.0,
      "end_time": 174595.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: Absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174595.0,
      "end_time": 176230.0,
      "text": "And one of the fascinating things"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 176230.0,
      "end_time": 181630.0,
      "text": "is the whole use of language and translation, because what"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181630.0,
      "end_time": 183430.0,
      "text": "if you are migrant and you do not"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183430.0,
      "end_time": 185800.0,
      "text": "understand the language of the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 185800.0,
      "end_time": 187650.0,
      "text": "into which you&#39;ve migrated?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 187650.0,
      "end_time": 191230.0,
      "text": "To have good translation that&#39;s consistent --"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191230.0,
      "end_time": 193940.0,
      "text": "these questions have always fascinated me."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 193940.0,
      "end_time": 197829.0,
      "text": "And I think those were some of the issues that attracted me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 197830.0,
      "end_time": 200830.0,
      "text": "at the beginning, trying to think about this much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 200830.0,
      "end_time": 201880.0,
      "text": "broadly."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 201880.0,
      "end_time": 204220.0,
      "text": "So there are all these questions in the humanities"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 204220.0,
      "end_time": 207924.0,
      "text": "that fit into this larger issue of migration."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207924.0,
      "end_time": 209590.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: I guess another question"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 209590.0,
      "end_time": 211673.0,
      "text": "is, you know, what does it mean to be an American?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 211673.0,
      "end_time": 216610.0,
      "text": "And what does it mean to be French in periods of rising"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 216610.0,
      "end_time": 218110.0,
      "text": "and large-scale immigration?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 218110.0,
      "end_time": 221200.0,
      "text": "How do narratives change?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 221200.0,
      "end_time": 224450.0,
      "text": "And I know that scholars of literature are studying that."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 224450.0,
      "end_time": 225170.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: Absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 225170.0,
      "end_time": 227410.0,
      "text": "I mean, the question of narratives and narratives"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 227410.0,
      "end_time": 230920.0,
      "text": "of migration is absolutely huge and crosses the disciplines."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 230920.0,
      "end_time": 232823.0,
      "text": "And we each look at it very differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 232824.0,
      "end_time": 234490.0,
      "text": "But if you think of, as you were saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 234490.0,
      "end_time": 237700.0,
      "text": "the narratives that tell us our nationhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 237700.0,
      "end_time": 241209.0,
      "text": "or why governments choose certain programs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 241210.0,
      "end_time": 242890.0,
      "text": "migration programs -- then there are also"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 242890.0,
      "end_time": 245190.0,
      "text": "the journalistsâ€™ stories that try"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 245200.0,
      "end_time": 249100.0,
      "text": "to get very close to the migrant lives and can be short"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 249100.0,
      "end_time": 250420.0,
      "text": "or in book form."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 250420.0,
      "end_time": 253630.0,
      "text": "And then there are, of course, all the literary narratives --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 253630.0,
      "end_time": 257180.0,
      "text": "literary and filmic, visual arts, music --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 257180.0,
      "end_time": 259890.0,
      "text": "that explore other aspects of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 259890.0,
      "end_time": 262296.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a huge question -- a huge cultural question."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 262296.0,
      "end_time": 263170.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 263170.0,
      "end_time": 265120.0,
      "text": "And one of the exciting things about the research community"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 265120.0,
      "end_time": 267536.0,
      "text": "is that scholars bring all of these different perspectives"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 267536.0,
      "end_time": 268960.0,
      "text": "to bear."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 268960.0,
      "end_time": 271960.0,
      "text": "I mean, some people are unnerved by these changes in what it"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 271960.0,
      "end_time": 273234.0,
      "text": "means to be an American."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273235.0,
      "end_time": 273715.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: Of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 273715.0,
      "end_time": 274450.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: But the American story"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 274450.0,
      "end_time": 275710.0,
      "text": "is one of constant change."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 275710.0,
      "end_time": 277169.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: Absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 277170.0,
      "end_time": 278800.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: And it&#39;s great strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 278800.0,
      "end_time": 280432.0,
      "text": "that we have an immigrant history."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 280432.0,
      "end_time": 281890.0,
      "text": "SANDRA BERMANN: It&#39;s so interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 281890.0,
      "end_time": 285280.0,
      "text": "to hear what other national perspectives are on this, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 285280.0,
      "end_time": 287890.0,
      "text": "can be very different, and to have people in our research"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 287890.0,
      "end_time": 291390.0,
      "text": "community who are working on, you know, the Pacific Asian"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 291400.0,
      "end_time": 294760.0,
      "text": "world, who are working on Europe and also"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 294760.0,
      "end_time": 297340.0,
      "text": "Latin America and the U.S. and many other parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 297340.0,
      "end_time": 298600.0,
      "text": "the Middle East."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 298600.0,
      "end_time": 301469.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s really very interesting comparatively, as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 301469.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "in terms of region."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 302460.0,
      "text": "STEPHEN MACEDO: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 302460.0,
      "end_time": 305530.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve got here some of the best scholars in the Woodrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 305530.0,
      "end_time": 308469.0,
      "text": "Wilson School, sociology, political science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 308470.0,
      "end_time": 311860.0,
      "text": "in my neck of the woods, also -- philosophy, economics --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 311860.0,
      "end_time": 314890.0,
      "text": "working on both the empirical and the moral dimensions"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 314890.0,
      "end_time": 315909.0,
      "text": "of these questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 315910.0,
      "end_time": 320220.0,
      "text": "And I look forward to, you know, doing more."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 320220.0,
      "end_time": 322670.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    }
  ]
